<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="admit-v">admit <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /əd'mɪt/    美 /əd'mɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>容许...进入</strong></h4>
<p>to allow sb / sth to enter a place：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A hole in the top of the roof admitted the light.
房顶的小洞能透进光线。</p><footer>2010 福建改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Only ticket-holders will be <strong>admitted to / into</strong> the stadium. 
持票者方可进入体育场。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>接纳；招收</strong></h4>
<p>to allow sb to become a member of a club, a school, etc.：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I shall be very likely to <strong>be admitted to</strong> my dream university.
我很有可能会被我梦想的大学录取。</p><footer>2014 四川</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The table-tennis team of our school is admitting new players.
我们学校的乒乓球队正在招收新队员。</p><footer>2017 全国书面表达</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>承认</strong></h4>
<p>to agree, often unwillingly, that sth is true：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>“I can’t sing at all,” he freely / openly / frankly admitted.
“我不会唱歌，”他坦率 / 公开 / 坦白承认说。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We should have the courage to <strong>admit</strong> (to) our mistakes<strong>to_2</strong>
我们应当有勇气承认错误。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I had to <strong>admit</strong> (to) <strong>being</strong> nervous about the test<strong>to_2</strong>
我不得不承认对这次考试感到紧张。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I don't really like the author, although I have to admit his books are very exciting.
尽管我不太喜欢这位作者，但不得不承认他的书还是很激动人心。</p><footer>2014 山东</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>供认</strong></h4>
<p>to say that you have done sth wrong or illegal：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He refused to <strong>admit</strong> (to) the other charges<strong>to_2</strong>
他拒不承认其他指控。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>admitted ( to ) having</strong> stolen / <strong>stealing</strong> the car.
她供认偷了那辆车。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>admittedly /əd'mɪtɪdli/ adv   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The technique is painful, admittedly, but it benefits the patient greatly.
这项技术诚然会有些痛苦，但是病人会大大受益。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>If you leave the club, you will not <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (admit)back in.   （2009 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. be admitted  </p></div>